      public void addCompleterValue(int index, String value)
      Adds a value to index of tab completer. Note that completer values will be automatically sorted using completerSort(List, String[]) AFTER tabComplete(CommandSender, String[]) is called.
      Parameters:
      index - - Index. Stars at 1 for first argument (args[0])
      value - - Value to add. Will be forced to lower case.
